data.description: Turn Key, Three bedroom, very well cared for, year round lakeside home on Round Pond in Charlotte. Large open living room and kitchen area that opens on to full length deck with stairs to level backyard with fire pit and nice dock. There is also an unfinished guest cottage. Home comes with all furnishings, generator, and 300 feet of frontage on the pond.  Second to last house on the dead end lane, lots of privacy and a great view across the lake along with great fishing, kayaking and swimming.
